@autowired -> spring will inject this dep   types > field injection , setter , constructor


@Controller ->  used only on a class that this class acts as a controller / used to mark a class as a web request handler / dispatcher  scans such classes 
for mapped methods and detects @RequestMapping

@SpringBootApplication -> to mark the main class of the spring application it contains ( @Configuration, @EnableAutoConfiguration, and @ComponentScan )

@EnableAsync -> enable aysc fx 
